          "subtype": "ability",
          "text": "An aeon stone swarm is surrounded by a pall of magical interference, which hampers spellcasting in the area. Whenever a creature in the aura attempts to Cast a Spell, they must succeed at a DC 5 flat check or the spell is disrupted.",
